# Support

Thank you for using **Revise**!  

If you encounter any issues, have questions, or want to provide feedback, please contact our support team:

**Email:** [study.inc.dev@gmail.com](mailto:study.inc.dev@gmail.com)  

We aim to respond to all inquiries as quickly as possible.  

## Reporting Bugs

When reporting a bug, please include:  
- Steps to reproduce the issue  
- Screenshots or screen recordings (if possible)  
- Your device and app version  

## Feature Requests

We love hearing your ideas! Please send us a detailed description of the feature you’d like to see, and we’ll consider it for future updates.  

## Community

Feel free to check out discussions, FAQs, or contribute to the project on [GitHub Discussions](#) (if applicable).  

Thank you for helping make **Revise** even better!
